column5: http://peterborough.kijiji.ca/c-cars-vehicles-boats-watercraft-canoes-kayaks-paddle-LARGE-ALUMINUM-CANOE-FOR-SALE-BUILT-TO-HOUSE-MOTOR-ON-THE-BACK-W0QQAdIdZ388649910  175 bucks ain't bad. Not my boat and don't know anything about it. I just know somebody always seems to be looking for one.
